info.name: TTPD taylor swift
info.description: Taylor Swift's new album "The Tortured Poets Department" picture.
info.additionalInfo: Taylor Swift's new album "The Tortured Poets Department" better known as "TTPD" is her 11th album. 24 albums in all, if you include her re-recordings. Taylor swift(debut), Fearless, Speak Now, Red, 1989,  Reputation, Lover, Folklore, Evermore, Midnights, and TTPD. Her re-recordings: Debut (TV) Fearless (TV), Speak Now (TV), Red (TV) 1989 (TV) and  Reputation (TV). Us swifties are still waiting for Reputation (TV) and Taylor swift/ debut (TV).
